dified to meet specific demands in a particular region.&#34;,&#34;downloadBrochureText&#34;:&#34;Download brochure&#34;,&#34;downloadBrochureLink&#34;:&#34;assets/images/documentation/2021_700CL-X SPORT brochure_EU.pdf&#34;,&#34;downloadName&#34;:&#34;2021_700CL-X SPORT brochure_EU.pdf&#34;,&#34;motorcycleType&#34;:&#34;MOTORCYCLE&#34;,&#34;pointData&#34;:[{&#34;title&#34;:&#34;NEO RETRO SPORTINESS&#34;,&#34;name&#34;:&#34;dot-point0&#34;,&#34;des&#34;:&#34;The fuel tank is designed with stickers lacquered onto it, including the unique logo of 700CL-X SPORT The paint is bright, beautiful, and durable. The front of the fuel tank and rear of the bike is decorated with carbon fiber texture panels, which give it a SPORTier look. The material processing of the footpeg guard is consistent with the fuel tank, giving it an overall unified look. These design elements make the ingenious 700CL-X SPORT even more unique.&#34;,&#34;img&#34;:&#34;assets/images/关键部位图/20210902154426.png&#34;,&#34;number&#34;:&#34;/etc/designs/cfmoto/assets/product/category/01@2x.jpg&#34;},{&#34;title&#34;:&#34;ENGINE&#34;,&#34;name&#34;:&#34;dot-point1&#34;,&#34;des&#34;:&#34;The engine is a liquid-cooled,693cc,two-cylinder four-stroke DOHC inline engine. lt has a bore of 83mm and a stroke of 64mm and favors smooth acceleration at all rpm and ease of handling. The engine produces its maximum 55kW/75HP output at 8,500rpm and maximum 68N-m torque at 6,500rpm. The optimized intake system improves airflow efficiency for quick-revving power and precise throttle response, making it easy to accelerate and overtake. The engine has lightweight pistons and DLC coating to minimize friction.The X-shape engraved on the engine cover also enhanced the aesthetics&#34;,&#34;img&#34;:&#34;assets/images/关键部位图/20210903082715.png&#34;,&#34;number&#34;:&#34;/etc/designs/cfmoto/assets/product/category/02@2x.jpg&#34;},{&#34;title&#34;:&#34;RIDING MODES&#34;,&#34;name&#34;:&#34;dot-point2&#34;,&#34;des&#34;:&#34;700CL-X is fitted with two riding modes, SPORT and ECO SPORT mode, for full engine power and sharp throttle response;ECO mode, for softer throttle response and fuel efficiency.&#34;,&#34;img&#34;:&#34;assets/images/关键部位图/20210902154336.png&#34;,&#34;number&#34;:&#34;/etc/designs/cfmoto/assets/product/category/03@2x.jpg&#34;},{&#34;title&#34;:&#34;CRUISE-CONTROL&#34;,&#34;name&#34;:&#34;dot-point3&#34;,&#34;des&#34;:&#34;When the vehicle speed is greater than 40km/h, the driver can toggle on the cruise control. With the help of the cruise control system, the 700CL-X SPORT automatically maintains the speed, thus reducing the rider fatigue and making riding more comfortable. The speed can be increased or decreased through the RES and SET buttons, and the maximum vehicle speed is limited to 120km/h.&#34;,&#34;img&#34;:&#34;assets/images/关键部位图/20210902154336.png&#34;,&#34;number&#34;:&#34;/etc/designs/cfmoto/assets/product/category/04@2x.jpg&#34;},{&#34;title&#34;:&#34;CF-SC SLIPPER CLUTCH&#34;,&#34;name&#34;:&#34;dot-point4&#34;,&#34;des&#34;:&#34;The CF-SC slipper clutch helps enlarge the power buffering and enhance the smoothness of shifting, thereby reducing the engine braking impact during downshifts, improving safety and riding comfort.&#34;,&#34;img&#34;:&#34;assets/images/关键部位图/20210902154316.png&#34;,&#34;number&#34;:&#34;/etc/designs/cfmoto/assets/product/category/05@2x.jpg&#34;}]}" variant="[{&#34;image&#34;:&#34;assets/images/700CL-X-SPORT_Nebula-White.png&#34;,&#34;title&#34;:&#34;Nebula-White&#34;,&#34;desc&#34;:&#34;&#34;,&#34;modelColor&#34;:&#34;&#34;,&#34;colorImage&#34;:&#34;assets/images/Nebula White (1).png&#34;},{&#34;image&#34;:&#34;assets/images/700CL-X-SPORT_Velocity-Grey.png&#34;,&#34;title&#34;:&#34;Velocity-Grey&#34;,&#34;desc&#34;:&#34;&#34;,&#34;modelColor&#34;:&#34;&#34;,&#34;colorImage&#34;:&#34;assets/images/Velocity Grey.png&#34;}]"/>
